name: DAOKing
description: From COVID-19 to Delta, to Omicron, people around the world have been devastated by the epidemic. In order to commemorate the global war epidemic in 2021, the anti-epidemic actions of the future world, and the inaction of those in power, those who survived the ravages of the virus established DAOKing, and 90% of the profit of DAOKing's future applications will be distributed on December 25 (the birthday of Jesus) every year. ) donated to the International Red Cross for the war against the epidemic under the normal epidemic situation.
payDisclosure: Do your own research and understand the risks before committing your funds.
